			<h4><a id="comment_link_64156011" name="comment_link_64156011" href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23191801&amp;cid=64156011" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64156011)" >Re:Ah yes, "stifling" innovation</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64156011" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64156011); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Funny)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~fahrbot-bot">fahrbot-bot</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~fahrbot-bot">( 874524 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
