</p><p>The American Petroleum Institute needs to understand that there are those who want to stifle their entire industry right into non existence. Clean up your act, or you'll just provide your enemies with more political ammunition.
</p><p>You were given a $1 billion carrot. Now here comes the stick.</p></div>
